{"tid":1752211,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"［翻盤］我嗰區贏咗，想大家一齊多謝下屋企人","createTime":"2019-11-24T19:20:43.000Z","updateTime":"2019-11-25T16:08:02.000Z","uid":113113,"like":44,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"be5ac6d63f55e19493d294ed1e4ecb966e1bf1c6","tid":1752211,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:20:43.000Z","msg":"話說我嗰區一向都係藍嘅當選。<br />\n民賤聯嘅親戚朋友義工呢排都不斷打電話又洗樓叫屋企人投藍。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/on_hold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n本身公公婆婆係政治冷感，爸爸媽媽仲要係淺藍。<br />\n<br />\n我呢幾個月都不厭其煩，好詳盡解釋事件，同佢哋講政府點點點衰法。<br />\n佢哋態度都有開始軟化，但一直都話自己唔會投票。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/no.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身區選都諗住放棄說服佢哋投黃，由得佢哋唔投，但估唔到前一晚爸爸竟然主動問我要投邊個！<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n佢話想支持我，嗰刻真係好感動。<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n連平時行動不便唔出街嘅公公婆婆都願意坐輪椅跟我出去投黃。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n本身我諗住民賤聯宣傳得咁恆，都打定輸數，諗住至少我已經贏咗頭家。<br />\n但頭先睇到結果係贏咗，真係感動到喊咗出來<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n要贏，就全家一齊贏！<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n亦想趁呢個機會同大家講，唔好放棄屋企人。<br />\n即使我屋企人都係移民落來香港，但都可以connect<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n比起聽民賤聯義工鳩up，其實中年老年人都會寧願撐自己仔女先<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/play.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n光復香港，時代革命！<br />\n<br />\nBtw 望住啲民賤聯義工奶哂鞋底咁多謝我公公婆婆投佢，真係好爽<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"098654b8edd0e4d81dc801cb810ae05bd230406f","tid":1752211,"uid":113113,"like":6,"dislike":0,"score":6,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:25:01.000Z","msg":"今日投票都見到中年老年人係多過後生，但結果勝出，證明好多都係支持緊我哋。<br />\n<br />\n記得要好好多謝佢哋呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b4763e536e6bd2198fb91f6ba5e65916e50b5ebc","tid":1752211,"uid":113113,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:26:34.000Z","msg":"平時都多啲同佢啲溝通，因為佢哋圈子真係好多fake news同埋充滿cctvb<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/heard.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n要帶佢哋認清真相<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7f7abd8c69148519047a7fe4d347e9ec03dda58","tid":1752211,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:44:57.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"506f2888c86601e12f3ad24866402347cc8c7868","tid":1752211,"uid":49018,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:45:17.000Z","msg":"幫你推"},{"pid":"d208719dc908c9d46fca0ca1408647b528bd5e9a","tid":1752211,"uid":269452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:45:59.000Z","msg":"多謝香港人，一齊企出嚟 <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1c69aa284b9f061615ab10f586af8fb925b11aff","tid":1752211,"uid":334938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:47:49.000Z","msg":"我媽都被我說服到由冷感變淺黃再投埋處女票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"a0b679a981c7d94a5ad07e5e9e4b670c03ac8599","tid":1752211,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"1c69aa284b9f061615ab10f586af8fb925b11aff","tid":1752211,"uid":334938,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T19:47:49.000Z","msg":"我媽都被我說服到由冷感變淺黃再投埋處女票<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-24T22:52:26.000Z","msg":"多謝伯母寶貴嘅一票<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wine.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n親情嘅力量好重要！"},{"pid":"8fc1e8df017133ed0972b12e2dcc0dda8510a599","tid":1752211,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"d208719dc908c9d46fca0ca1408647b528bd5e9a","tid":1752211,"uid":269452,"like":0,"di