11,"uid":230389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T11:29:14.000Z","msg":"阿媽港豬淺藍，有次dum曬我啲物資，但為咗我去咗投票<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:07:21.000Z","msg":"We connect <img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n始終都係企仔女呢邊<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ea6e73d2156d789a7012e149176258712908101","tid":1752211,"uid":113113,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"227bdb8df77046a69e3229a3320986ce97ca6b30","tid":1752211,"uid":13661,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T13:10:09.000Z","msg":"堅持才會見到希望<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/clap.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-11-25T16:08:02.000Z","msg":"努力文宣<br />\n連啲長者都話黑警暴行太過份<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/argue.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}]}